# Local SQLite working files (hlp-*, including -info, -shm, -wal variants).
# Anchored to repo root so we don't accidentally swallow legitimately-named
# files under subdirectories (e.g. server/systemd/hlp-blocklist-refresh.*).
/hlp-*

# Python cache
